#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &skanlite;"
msgstr "&skanlite; kasutamine"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scanner Selection"
msgstr "Skanneri valimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A default scanner can be specified on the command line of &skanlite; using "
"<userinput>skanlite -d [device name]</userinput> in a terminal. If the "
"selected scanner cannot be opened or if no default scanner is provided, a "
"scanner selection dialog is opened."
msgstr ""
"Vaikimisi skanneri saab määrata &skanlite; käsureal, andes terminalis käsu "
"<userinput>skanlite -d [seadme nimi]</userinput>. Kui valitud skannerit ei "
"saa avada või kui vaikeskannerit ei ole antud, avatakse skanneri valimise "
"dialoog."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&skanlite; scanner selection dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&skanlite; skanneri valimise dialoog</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&skanlite; scanner selection dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&skanlite; skanneri valimise dialoog</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The user can choose the scanner to be used and press <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> to open the scanner. Pressing <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> will "
"cause &skanlite; to exit."
msgstr ""
"Kasutaja saab valida vajaliku skanneri ning klõpsata <guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> selle avamiseks. Kui klõpsata <guibutton>Loobu</guibutton>, "
"lõpetab &skanlite; töö."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>No scanner found</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skannerit ei leitud</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>No scanner found</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skannerit ei leitud</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case no devices were found, maybe because the scanner is not plugged in "
"or switched off, correct that. Then the <guibutton>Reload device list</"
"guibutton> can be used to reload the list of scanners."
msgstr ""
"Kui seadmeid ei leita, võib põhjus olla selles, et skanner ei ole ühendatud "
"või on välja lülitatud. See viga tuleb parandada. Seejärel saab skannerite "
"nimekirja taaslaadimiseks kasutada nuppu <guibutton>Laadi seadmete nimekiri "
"uuesti</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Not all drivers/backends support this feature. In that case quit &skanlite;, "
"connect your scanner and restart the application."
msgstr ""
"Seda võimalust ei toeta kõik draiverid/taustaprogrammid. Sellisel juhul "
"lõpeta &skanlite; töö, ühenda skanner ja käivita rakendus uuesti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "&skanlite; Main Window"
msgstr "&skanlite; peaaken"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&skanlite; main window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&skanlite; peaaken</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&skanlite; main window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&skanlite; peaaken</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the main window, the user has two sets of scan options: <guilabel>Basic "
"Options</guilabel> and <guilabel>Scanner Specific Options</guilabel>. The "
"<guilabel>Basic Options</guilabel> tab contains the most common parameters "
"that the SANE scanner backends provide, while the <guilabel>Scanner Specific "
"Options</guilabel> tab contains all the options of the backend. The options "
"listed here depend on SANE support for your driver: libksane (which "
"&skanlite; uses) should be able to display most of the types of parameters "
"that SANE provides (analog gamma tables are not supported at this time)."
msgstr ""
"Peaaknas on kasutaja päralt kaks skannimisvalikute komplekti: "
"<guilabel>põhivalikud</guilabel> ja <guilabel>skanneri valikud</guilabel>. "
"<guilabel>Põhivalikute</guilabel> kaart sisaldab peamisi parameetreid, mida "
"pakuvad SANE skanneri taustaprogrammid, <guilabel>skanneri valikute</"
"guilabel> kaart aga kõiki taustaprogrammi valikuid. Nähaolevad valikud "
"sõltuvad sellest, kuidas SANE sinu draiverit toetab: libksane, mida "
"&skanlite; tarvitab, peaks suutma näidata kõiki peamisi parameetreid, mida "
"SANE üldse pakub (praegu ei ole toetatud analooggammatabelid)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Scanner Specific Options tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skanneri valikute kaart</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Scanner Specific Options tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skanneri valikute kaart</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The scanner specific options contains more detailed options of the backends. "
"&skanlite; (libksane) does not have any special handling for these options."
msgstr ""
"Skanneri valikud sisaldavad taustaprogrammide üksikasjalikumaid valikuid. "
"&skanlite; ehk täpsemalt libksane ei lisa neile midagi omalt poolt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are satisfied with your settings, you can use the little arrow on the "
"top of the options splitter. When clicked it collapses or expands the "
"options. The collapser can overlap the preview area, but fades away when the "
"mouse cursor moves out of the collapser."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled seadistustega rahul, võid kasutada väikest noolekest valikute "
"eraldaja kohal. Sellele klõpsates keritakse valikud kokku või lahti. "
"Kokkukerimisel võib see katta eelvaatluse ala, kuid kaob nähtavalt, kui viia "
"hiir selle kohalt minema."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scanning"
msgstr "Skannimine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To scan an image, the user can start with a preview scan and then select the "
"part of the scan area to do the final scan on. The preview scan is started "
"by pressing the preview button."
msgstr ""
"Pildi skannimiseks tuleb alustada eelvaatluse skannimisega ja seejärel "
"valida osa, mis lõplikult skannida. Eelvaatluse skannimiseks tuleb klõpsata "
"eelvaatluse nupule."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Preview Button</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Eelvaatluse nupp</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Preview Button</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Eelvaatluse nupp</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the preview is scanned the area for the final image can be selected."
msgstr ""
"Kui eelvaatlus on skannitud, saab sellel valida välja lõpliku pildi ala."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Selection and zoom</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Valik ja suurendus</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Selection and zoom</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Valik ja suurendus</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To better select the image the user can zoom in, out, to the current "
"selection or zoom to fit the whole preview to the window."
msgstr ""
"Pildi paremaks valimiseks saab eelvaatlust vastavalt vajadusele suurendada "
"ja vähendada."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The \"zoom to fit\" button</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Aknasse mahutamise nupp</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The \"zoom to fit\" button</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Aknasse mahutamise nupp</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the image is selected the final image can be acquired by pressing the "
"final scan button."
msgstr ""
"Kui pildiala on välja valitud, saab lõpliku pildi valmistada klõpsuga "
"lõpliku pildi skannimise nupule."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The final scan button</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Lõpliku pildi skannimise nupp</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The final scan button</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Lõpliku pildi skannimise nupp</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "You will see the progress of the scan."
msgstr "Kasutajale näidatakse skannimise edenemist."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Scanning in progress</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Skannimise edenemine</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Scanning in progress</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Skannimise edenemine</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If <guilabel>Preview before saving</guilabel> is selected in the "
#| "settings, the scanned image is displayed in a preview window as you can "
#| "see below on the screenshot. If <guibutton>Save</guibutton> is pressed, "
#| "the image is saved and if <guibutton>Close</guibutton> is pressed the "
#| "preview is discarded and you return to the main window."
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Preview before saving</guilabel> is selected in the settings, "
"the scanned image is displayed in a preview window as you can see below on "
"the screenshot. If <guibutton>Save</guibutton> is pressed, the image is "
"saved and if <guibutton>Discard</guibutton> is pressed the preview is "
"discarded and you return to the main window."
msgstr ""
"Kui seadistustes on valitud <guilabel>Eelvaatlus enne salvestamist</"
"guilabel>, kuvatakse skannitud pilti eelvaatluse aknas, nagu näitab ka "
"siinne pilt. Klõpsates nupule <guibutton>Salvesta</guibutton>, pilt "
"salvestatakse, klõpsuga nupule <guibutton>Sulge</guibutton> eelvaatlus "
"unustatakse ning naastakse peaaknasse."

