#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scanning Multiple Selections"
msgstr "Skannimine mitme valikuga"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes you need only certain parts of an image. Instead of scanning the "
"whole picture and then using a graphics application (&eg; &kolourpaint;) to "
"save the different image parts into separate files, use &skanlite;'s "
"multiple selection feature."
msgstr ""
"Mõnikord võib vaja minna ainult kindlat osa pildist. Selmet skannida kogu "
"pilt ja kasutada seejärel mõnda graafikarakendust (nt. &kolourpaint;) pildi "
"eri osade salvestamiseks eri failidesse, võib kasutada &skanlite; mitme "
"valiku võimalust. "

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Multiple Selections</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Mitu valikut</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Multiple Selections</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Mitu valikut</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scan a preview and then use the &LMB; to select the first part of the image "
"in the preview. Hover the selected area with mouse cursor and click on the "
"green <guiicon>+</guiicon> icon to select the area. Selected areas are "
"indicated by a red border. Now select the next parts of the image in the "
"same way."
msgstr ""
"Skanni eelvaatlus ning vali &HVNga; eelvaatluses pildi esimene osa. "
"Hiirekursoriga valitud ala kohal viibides klõpsa rohelisele ikoonile "
"<guiicon>+</guiicon>, millega ala valitakse. Valitud ala näitab punane "
"piire. Nüüd võid samamoodi valida pildi ülejäänud osad."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a single selection hover the area with the mouse cursor and click "
"on the red <guiicon>-</guiicon> icon. With <guilabel>Clear Selections</"
"guilabel> from the context menu launched with the &RMB; all selections in a "
"preview can be removed."
msgstr ""
"Konkreetse valiku eemaldamiseks vii hiirekursor ala kohale ja klõpsa "
"punasele ikoonile <guiicon>-</guiicon>. Kui avada &HPNga; kontekstimenüü, "
"saab sealse käsuga <guilabel>Puhasta valikud</guilabel> eemaldada kõik "
"eelvaatluses tehtud valikud."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you placed two separate images or photos on you scanner and started a "
"preview &skanlite; automatically preselect the different areas. This "
"behaviour can be switched off in the settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Kui asetasid skannerisse kaks eraldi pilti või fotot ja käivitasid "
"eelvaatluse, valib &skanlite; automaatselt eri alad. Sellist käitumist saab "
"välja lülitada seadistustedialoogis."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are satisfied with your choice starting the final batch scan of all "
"selections. The images are saved using the batch renaming feature described "
"in the settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled valikuga rahul, alusta kõigi valikute lõpliku hulgiskannimisega. "
"Pildid salvestatakse hulgi-ümbernimetamise võimalust kasutades, mida "
"kirjeldatakse seadistustedialoogi juures."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "&skanlite; settings"
msgstr "&skanlite; seadistused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By clicking the <guibutton>Settings</guibutton> button, the settings dialog "
"is brought up before the main window. You can choose the most important "
"settings here."
msgstr ""
"Klõpsuga nupule <guibutton>Seadistused</guibutton> avatakse "
"seadistustedialoog, milles saab paika panna rakenduse tähtsamad seadistused."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &skanlite; settings dialog"
msgstr "&skanlite; seadistustedialoog näeb välja selline"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "&skanlite; settings dialog"
msgstr "&skanlite; seadistustedialoog"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview before saving:"
msgstr "Eelvaatlus enne salvestamist:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The user can chose to preview the image before saving. In this case the "
"<guilabel>Preview before saving</guilabel> option can be left checked. If "
"the user does not want to preview the image this option should then be "
"unchecked."
msgstr ""
"Kasutaja võib lasta enne salvestamist endale pilti näidata. Sel juhul tuleks "
"ära märkida valik <guilabel>Eelvaatlus enne salvestamist</guilabel>. Kui "
"seda ei soovita, siis ei ole muidugi vaja ka kastikest märkida."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save Mode:"
msgstr "Salvestamisviis:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This setting allows you to choose how &skanlite; will save the images. If "
#| "you choose <guilabel>Open the save dialog for every image</guilabel> then "
#| "the save dialog will be opened for every scanned image. If you prefer "
#| "&skanlite; to auto-save (by auto-generating a name and saving the image "
#| "in a predefined folder) then you can choose <guilabel>Save without asking "
#| "for a filename</guilabel> or <guilabel>Open the save dialog for the first "
#| "image only</guilabel>."
msgid ""
"This setting allows you to choose how &skanlite; will save the images. If "
"you choose <guilabel>Open the save dialog for every image</guilabel> the "
"save dialog will be opened for every scanned image. If you prefer &skanlite; "
"to auto-save (by auto-generating a name and saving the image in a predefined "
"folder) you can choose <guilabel>Open the save dialog for the first image "
"only</guilabel>. This option will open the following \"Save Location\" "
"dialog for the first scanned image."
msgstr ""
"See võimaldab valida, kuidas &skanlite; pildid salvestab. Kui valida "
"<guilabel>Salvestamisdialoogi avamine iga pildi puhul</guilabel>, avataksegi "
"iga skannitud pildi puhul salvestamisdialoog. Kui aga eelistad, et "
"&skanlite; salvestaks automaatselt sinu eest (luues ise nime ja salvestades "
"pildid eelnevalt määratud kataloogi), vali <guilabel>Salvestamine failinime "
"pärimata</guilabel> või <guilabel>Salvestamisdialoogi avamine ainult esimese "
"pildi puhul</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:326
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Here's a screenshot of &skanlite; settings dialog"
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &skanlite; save location dialog"
msgstr "&skanlite; seadistustedialoog näeb välja selline"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:332
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "&skanlite; settings dialog"
msgid "&skanlite; Save Location dialog."
msgstr "&skanlite; seadistustedialoog"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save Location:"
msgstr "Salvestamiskoht:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This setting defines where the images should be saved when <guilabel>Save "
#| "without asking for a filename</guilabel> is chosen in the previous "
#| "option. If the save dialog is to be opened for every image the default "
#| "save location for the dialog will be the same as this parameter. The "
#| "default save location is your home folder and you can change this "
#| "location by clicking on the <guibutton>...</guibutton> button."
msgid ""
"This setting defines the default save location and file naming. The default "
"save location is your home folder and you can change this location by "
"clicking on the <guibutton>...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab määrata, kuhu pildid salvestatakse, kui ülal on valitud "
"<guilabel>Salvestamine failinime pärimata</guilabel>. Aga ka siis, kui iga "
"pildi puhul avatakse salvestamisdialoog, kasutatakse siin määratud asukohta "
"tolles dialoogis vaikimisi etteantava asukohana. Üldiselt on vaikimisi "
"kataloogiks sinu kodukataloog, aga seda saab muuta, kui klõpsad nupule "
"<guibutton>...</guibutton>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name Format:"
msgstr "Nimi ja vorming:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This parameter defines the image prefix for the auto-saved images and is "
"also the suggested name for the image in the save dialog. The auto-saved "
"image will have a numeric suffix (the ### will be replaced by numbers) that "
"is increased every time an image is saved."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab määrata pildile automaatsel salvestamisel antava eesliite ning ka "
"nime, mida pakutakse pildile salvestamisdialoogis. Automaatselt "
"salvestatavatel piltidel on arvudest järelliited (### asendatakse arvuga), "
"mis suurenevad iga salvestamiskorraga."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can also choose the save format of the file, default is png."
msgstr ""
"Samuti saab valida salvestatava pildi vormingu. Vaikimisi on selleks png."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify save quality:"
msgstr "Salvestamise kvaliteet:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The user can chose to specify the image quality to be used for saving the "
"images. The image quality setting affects the compression level used for "
"saving. If <guilabel>Specify save quality</guilabel> is not checked, the "
"quality is the default value chosen by &Qt;."
msgstr ""
"Kasutaja saab määrata, millise kvaliteediga pildid salvestatakse. See "
"mõjutab salvestamisel kasutatavat tihendustaset. Kui kastike "
"<guilabel>Salvestamise kvaliteet</guilabel> märkimata jätta, valitakse "
"kvaliteet &Qt; vaikimisi väärtuse põhjal."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set preview resolution (DPI)"
msgstr "Eelvaatluse eraldusvõime (DPI)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&skanlite; is using heuristics to try to get a sane resolution, but if that "
"fails and the resolution is too high or low, then the preview resolution can "
"be manually set with this option."
msgstr ""
"&skanlite; kasutab heuristikat SANE eraldusvõime hankimiseks, aga kui see "
"nurjub ning eraldusvõime on liiga suur või väike, saab selle valikuga "
"määrata eelvaatluse eraldusvõime käsitsi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disable automatic selections"
msgstr "Automaatse valimise keelamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default automatic selections are enabled; and after a preview, libksane "
"does try to automatically select the images in the preview and should batch "
"scan the selected areas. &eg; if you place two photos on the scanner and do "
"a preview, &skanlite; will automatically add selections of the photos."
msgstr ""
"Vaikimisi on automaatsed valikud lubatud ning pärast eelvaatlust üritab "
"libksane automaatselt valida eelvaatluses pildid ja hulgiskannida valitud "
"alad. Kui näiteks asetad skannerisse kaks fotot, siis nende eelvaatluse "
"puhul valib &skanlite; automaatselt  fotod."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If on the other hand you are usually scanning documents it might be that the "
"automatic selection will select a lot of different parts in the documents "
"and you have to manually remove the selections. To avoid that tick the "
"checkbox and disable automatic selection."
msgstr ""
"Kui aga sa tavaliselt skannid lihtsalt dokumente, siis võib automaatse "
"valiku korral valituks osutada hulk dokumendi eri osasid, mispuhul tuleb "
"hakata valikuid käsitsi eemaldama. Selle vältimiseks eemalda märkekastist "
"linnuke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "Revert scanner options to default values"
msgstr "Skanneri valikute lähtestamine vaikeväärtustele"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The last used settings are reloaded on startup. If you have screwed up the "
"options (for example if you have changed the color correction settings, "
"available in some backends, without knowing what they mean), the image can "
"start to look very odd. For that scenario this option provides a way to "
"revert the setting to the default values, which are a combination of backend "
"and libksane defaults."
msgstr ""
"Käivitamisel laaditakse uuesti viimati kasutatud seadistused. Kui oled "
"nendega määda pannud (näitkes muutnud mõne taustaprogrammi puhul "
"saadaolevaid värviparanduse seadistusi ilma täpsemalt teadmata, mida need "
"teevad), võib pilt päris veider välja näha. Sel juhul on selle valikuga "
"võimalik kehtestada seadistustele vaikimisi väärtused, mis koosnevad "
"taustaprogrammi ja libksane vaikeväärtustest."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help, About, Settings and Close"
msgstr "Abi, info, seadistused ja sulge"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the main window you find the <guibutton>Help</guibutton>, "
"<guibutton>About</guibutton>, <guibutton>Settings</guibutton> and "
"<guibutton>Close</guibutton> buttons."
msgstr ""
"Peaakna allservas leiab nupud <guibutton>Abi</guibutton>, <guibutton>Info</"
"guibutton>, <guibutton>Seadistused</guibutton> ja <guibutton>Sulge</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Main Window Buttons</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Peaakna nupud</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Main Window Buttons</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Peaakna nupud</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Help</guibutton> button brings up the &kde; Help center with "
"the &skanlite; manual. The <guibutton>About</guibutton> button brings up the "
"&kde; About dialog for &skanlite;. The <guibutton>Settings</guibutton> "
"button displays the settings dialog and the <guibutton>Close</guibutton> "
"button is used to exit &skanlite;."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Abi</guibutton> avab &kde; abikeskuse &skanlite; käsiraamatuga. "
"<guibutton>Info</guibutton> avab &kde; info dialoogi &skanlite; teabega. "
"<guibutton>Seadistused</guibutton> avab seadistustedialoogi ja "
"<guibutton>Sulge</guibutton> lõpetab &skanlite; töö."

